The frontend application is in the `frontend/` directory.
The frontend application is built with React, Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui.
The package manager is pnpm.

The frontend project structure:

```txt
.
└── frontend/             # Dr. Koala frontend application
    ├── assets/           # Static assets
    ├── components/       # Shared components
    │   └── ui/           # Basic UI components that built by shadcn/ui
    ├── hooks/            # Custom React hooks
    ├── modules/          # Page modules
    ├── pages/            # Next.js page routes
    ├── public/           # Static public assets
    ├── styles/           # Global styles
    ├── types/            # TypeScript types, interfaces
    ├── utils/            # Utility functions
    ├── .env.example      # Environment variables example
    ├── biome.json        # Biome configuration
    ├── components.json   # shadcn/ui components configuration
    ├── next.config.ts    # Next.js configuration
    ├── package.json      # Node.js package manager configuration
    └── tsconfig.json     # TypeScript configuration
```
